INSERT INTO notes VALUES('34f3e975-34dd-4789-a144-c1f13ef7af8b','',replace('Greetings of the day!\n\nThanks for providing me the opportunity to introduce about myself.\n\nMy name is Kishore Kumar. I am currently working as CV Engineer in Engineering & Research Services and my designation is Technical lead in HCLTech. I completed my Master’s in Artificial  Intelligence from IIT Jodhpur under Computer Science Department and I am a technology enthusiast and interested in Problem Solving,machine learning,Deep Learning and Web development.I completed my Bachelor’s in Computer Science and Engineering with CGPA of 8 pointer from Sree Vidyanikethan Engineering College and I am basically from Tirupati Andhra Pradesh.Coming to my Family we are 4 my father a retired armed person and my mother home maker and my brother recently graduated. I worked for Tata Consultancy Services as system engineer for a while in BFSI domain where we are in a team of 9 worked on the Mainframe Systems,SQL and Informatica for task modelling and later transitioned my career plan to pursue higher studies.My hobbies include watching Cricket,playing chess and random surfing over Internet and solo riding. I am also a part of web development team of Student Wellbeing Committee in IIT Jodhpur and  also takes care of issues pertaining to the stress,mental balance and personal issues for the students under me.','\n',char(10)),'2024-03-30 09:49:13',NULL,'');
